org.spf4j.io.csv

Interface CsvReader


  • public interface CsvReader
    Char separated value file Reader. A newly created reader will initially be positioned at START_DOCUMENT. (current()) A example Token sequence will be: START_DOCUMENT, ELEMENT, ELEMENT, END_ROW, ELEMENT, ELEMENT, END_ROW, END_DOCUMENT
    Author:
    zoly
